longBusinessSummary: Falken Industries Ltd develops, manufactures, and commercializes various lines of cleaning and maintenance products for the consumer, professional, and industrial sectors primarily in European Community. Falken Industries Ltd was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Trenton, New Jersey.
